&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current date: 2026-06-23&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analysis target: 한국·미국 주식 후보 6개&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report mode: Candidate journal / public stock research notebook&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data timestamp: 2026-06-23 08:33 KST 기준. 한국 시세는 네이버 금융의 2026-06-22 장마감 표시값, 미국 시세는 CNBC와 공개 검색 결과의 2026-06-22 전후 표시값 기준&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;주요 출처: &lt;a href="https://www.mk.co.kr/news/stock/12063304"&gt;매일경제 - AI 데이터센터 전력·냉각업체&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.sentv.co.kr/article/view/sentv202602110039"&gt;GST 세미콘 코리아 2026 보도&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://v.daum.net/v/20260303091804915"&gt;GST MWC 2026 보도&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://comp.fnguide.com/SVO2/ASP/SVD_Main.asp?pGB=1&amp;amp;gicode=A083450&amp;amp;cID=&amp;amp;MenuYn=Y&amp;amp;ReportGB=&amp;amp;NewMenuID=11&amp;amp;stkGb=701"&gt;FnGuide - GST&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://comp.fnguide.com/SVO2/ASP/SVD_Main.asp?pGB=1&amp;amp;gicode=A053080&amp;amp;cID=&amp;amp;MenuYn=Y&amp;amp;ReportGB=&amp;amp;NewMenuID=11&amp;amp;stkGb=701"&gt;FnGuide - 케이엔솔&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://comp.fnguide.com/SVO2/ASP/SVD_Main.asp?pGB=1&amp;amp;gicode=A119850&amp;amp;cID=&amp;amp;MenuYn=Y&amp;amp;ReportGB=&amp;amp;NewMenuID=11&amp;amp;stkGb=701"&gt;FnGuide - 지엔씨에너지&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://seekingalpha.com/article/4910216-vertiv-holdings-the-ai-data-center-cooling-leader-still-has-momentum"&gt;Vertiv Q1 2026 관련 공개 보도&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://investors.tranetechnologies.com/news-and-events/news-releases/news-release-details/2026/Trane-Technologies-Reports-Strong-First-Quarter-Results-Raises-Full-Year-Revenue-and-EPS-Guidance/default.aspx"&gt;Trane Technologies Q1 2026&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://ir.carrier.com/news/news-details/2026/Carrier-Reports-First-Quarter-2026-Results/default.aspx"&gt;Carrier Global Q1 2026&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/VRT"&gt;CNBC - VRT&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/TT"&gt;CNBC - TT&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/CARR"&gt;CNBC - CARR&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이 글은 투자 추천이 아니라 공개자료로 남기는 후보 선별 기록이다. 최근 1-2주에는 전력망 접속, AI 반도체 소재, K-뷰티, 방산, 원전, 광통신을 이미 다뤘다. 오늘은 같은 AI 인프라 안에서도 서버가 내뿜는 열을 어떻게 빼낼지, 즉 &lt;strong&gt;데이터센터 냉각과 열관리&lt;/strong&gt;로 범위를 좁혔다.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>퀀텀 리프 5-Step 정량 분석 보고서: IES Holdings (IESC)</title><link>https://hybridego.github.io/2026/06/22/ies-holdings-iesc-analysis/</link><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 08:34:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://hybridego.github.io/2026/06/22/ies-holdings-iesc-analysis/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Current date: 2026-06-22&lt;br&gt;
Analysis target: IES Holdings (IESC)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="퀀텀-리프-5-step-정량-분석-보고서-ies-holdings-iesc"&gt;퀀텀 리프 5-Step 정량 분석 보고서: IES Holdings (IESC)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;보고일: 2026-06-22&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;주요 출처: &lt;a href="https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1048268/000104826826000087/iesc-20260501.htm"&gt;IES Holdings FY2026 2Q 8-K&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1048268/000104826826000086/iesc-20260331.htm"&gt;IES Holdings FY2026 2Q 10-Q&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://data.sec.gov/api/xbrl/companyfacts/CIK0001048268.json"&gt;SEC Companyfacts CIK 1048268&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/IESC/"&gt;Yahoo Finance IESC&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.marketbeat.com/stocks/NASDAQ/IESC/"&gt;MarketBeat IESC&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.stocktitan.net/sec-filings/IESC/8-k-ies-holdings-inc-reports-material-event-09a90e962da9.html"&gt;StockTitan IESC 8-K mirror&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.stocktitan.net/sec-filings/IESC/form-4-ies-holdings-inc-insider-trading-activity-7f02d544fca7.html"&gt;StockTitan Form 4 요약&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이 글은 투자 권유가 아니다. 무료 공개자료와 지연 시세로 작성한 공개 리서치 노트다. 프로젝트별 마진, 고객별 데이터센터 노출, 내부자 매도 의도는 공개자료만으로 완전히 검증할 수 없다.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>오늘의 주식 후보 노트: AI 데이터센터 전력 접속</title><link>https://hybridego.github.io/2026/06/21/stock-candidate-note-ai-datacenter-grid-interconnection/</link><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 08:31:00 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://hybridego.github.io/2026/06/21/stock-candidate-note-ai-datacenter-grid-interconnection/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="오늘의-주식-후보-노트-ai-데이터센터-전력-접속"&gt;오늘의 주식 후보 노트: AI 데이터센터 전력 접속&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current date: 2026-06-21&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analysis target: 한국·미국 주식 후보 6개&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report mode: Candidate journal / public stock research notebook&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data timestamp: 2026-06-21 08:31 KST 기준. 한국 시세는 네이버 금융 API의 2026-06-19 장마감 표시값, 미국 시세는 2026-06-18 미국 정규장 마감 기준 공개 시세&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;주요 출처: &lt;a href="https://www.ferc.gov/news-events/news/ferc-launches-aggressive-targeted-action-speed-large-load-integration"&gt;FERC - large load integration&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://apnews.com/article/power-electricity-ai-plants-data-centers-grid-506e3d206871111f15c3c62fc5368be5"&gt;AP - AI data center grid order&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.taihan.com/news/pr/releaseDetail?idx=425"&gt;대한전선 1Q26 보도자료&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.hankyung.com/article/202604282289P"&gt;HD현대일렉트릭 1Q26 보도자료&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://comp.wisereport.co.kr/company/c1010001.aspx?cmp_cd=199820"&gt;제일일렉트릭 기업현황&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://investors.quantaservices.com/news-events/press-releases/detail/396/quanta-services-reports-first-quarter-2026-results"&gt;Quanta Services 1Q26&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://investors.atkore.com/investors/news/news-details/2026/Atkore-Inc--Announces-Second-Quarter-2026-Results/default.aspx"&gt;Atkore 2Q26&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.eaton.com/us/en-us/company/news-insights/news-releases/2026/eaton-reports-record-first-quarter-2026-results.html"&gt;Eaton 1Q26&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
